{"data":[{"date":"18:08 24/07","title":"Juventus v\u00e0 AC Milan s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i \"bom t\u1ea5n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/juventus-va-ac-milan-sap-trao-doi-bom-tan.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus 2018 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Gonzalo Higuain cho AC Milan n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Leonardo Bonucci theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan h\u1ecfi mua Gonzalo Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAC Milan \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus 2018 ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Higuain cho AC Milan n\u1ebfu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus 2018 ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Higuain cho AC Milan n\u1ebfu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Chuyen-nhuong-Juventus-2018-chi-ban-Higuain-cho-AC-Milan-neu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>AC Milan mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Higuain\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Higuain \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra t\u1edbi 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Mian \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Higuain. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a AC Milan, Leonardo, v\u00e0 Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Beppe Marotta c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Higuain.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1eeb 45 \u0111\u1ebfn 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Higuain, h\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Higuain n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Bonucci</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus 2018 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Gonzalo Higuain cho AC Milan n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 Leonardo Bonucci theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Higuain va Bonucci co the hoan doi vi tri\" title=\"Higuain v\u00e0 Bonucci c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/juventus-va-ac-milan-sap-trao-doi-bom-tan.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Higuain v\u00e0 Bonucci c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Rugani, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p trung v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i, Juventus bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n mua l\u1ea1i Bonucci.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Juventus b\u00e1n Bonucci cho AC Milan v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan, m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n 50 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAC Milan ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 Bonucci tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus, song \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh tham v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu Higuain kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn trao \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p AC Milan kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 Bonucci, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. C\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-morata-neu-roi-chelsea-172-191433.html\" target=\"_blank\">AC Milan quan t\u00e2m Morata</span>, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4585","checkdouble":"191928"},{"date":"06:49 25/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: AS Roma \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng 1/8","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-as-roma-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-robin-olsen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ebfn 1/8 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Alisson Becker, AS Roma \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Robin Olsen t\u1eeb Copenhagen.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Robin Olsen<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e1n Alisson Becker cho Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 72.5 tri\u1ec7u euro, AS Roma kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Rome m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Robin Olsen t\u1eeb FC Copenhagen (\u0110an M\u1ea1ch) v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 8.5 tri\u1ec7u euro, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam 3.5 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 sau n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Robin Olsen  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Robin Olsen  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-as-roma-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-robin-olsen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>AS Roma chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Robin Olsen.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nFC Copenhagen s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 10% gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p AS Roma b\u00e1n Olsen trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai/ \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e3i to c\u1ee7a AS Roma khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao khi g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft, Robin Olsen cho bi\u1ebft: \"T\u00f4i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 vinh d\u1ef1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia nh\u1eadp AS Roma. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robin Olsen l\u00e0 ai?<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Malmo (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n), Olsen g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong khung g\u1ed7 FC Copenhagen \u1edf ba m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua. Olsen ra m\u1eaft \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 1/2015 v\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 23 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Monchi c\u1ee7a AS Roma chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y: \"Robin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn Roma. T\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t t\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, Olsen \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch hai l\u1ea7n, v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch hai l\u1ea7n. T\u1ea1i AS Roma, Olsen s\u1ebd mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 1.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a AS Roma:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom-180-191946.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Barcelona c\u01b0\u1edbp th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i AS Roma</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-thu-mon-petr-cech-172-191845.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mat-alisson-sep-roma-van-day-tu-tin-176-191624.html\">M\u1ea5t Alisson, s\u1ebfp Roma v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khong-the-gay-soc-vu-alisson-chelsea-chuyen-huong-sang-donnarumma-172-191596.html\">Chelsea chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n 19 tu\u1ed5i thay Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson: Khi \u201cbi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t\u201d t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-alisson-xac-nhan-roi-roma-toi-liverpool-voi-gia-sieu-khung-172-191549.html\">N\u00f3ng: Alisson x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Roma t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4584","checkdouble":"191948"},{"date":"21:19 24/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Cup T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/doi-thu-mang-luc-luong-rat-manh-sang-doi-dau-u23-viet-nam-tai-cup-tu-hung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, \u0110T U23 Palestine c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 mang m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>U23 Palestine mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Palestine mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U23 Palestine mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/nhan-dinh-u23-qatar-vs-u23-palestine-15h00-ngay-19-1-tu-ket-vck-u23-chau-a-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U23 Palestine mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb VFF, \u0110T U23 Palestine s\u1ebd mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t sang tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf - C\u00fap VinaPhone 2018. Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay 3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 U23 Oman, U23 Palestine, U23 Uzbekistan c\u00f9ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd d\u1ecbp quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u00e0o v\u00e0o ASIAD n\u00ean U23 Palestine mang theo qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua nh\u01b0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Abuaker, Fahkouri, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Alashhab, Farawi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Abuwada, Fannoun, Dabbagh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Yousef, Qymbor&hellip;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, trong chuy\u1ebfn sang Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a U23 Palestine c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Termanini (AFC Eskilstuna) v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 El-Kayed (CLB Prespa Birlik).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cao to, U23 Palestine \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao v\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i t\u1ea1i ASIAD. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y \u00c1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9i d\u1eadp U23 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-1, d\u00f9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i v\u1eeba v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch SEA Games 28. Do \u0111\u00f3, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p coi th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c mang t\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 anh h\u00e0o, U23 Palestine h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm&nbsp;t\u1ea1i Gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf U23 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<h2>Danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T U23 Palestine :</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n : Islam M.A.Masharqa</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng : Ayman R.K.Sangdouqa</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng : Husam.I.A.Younis, Osama K.M.Abualla, Anan W.A.Saleh</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e1c s\u0129 v\u1eadt l\u00fd tr\u1ecb li\u1ec7u : Mustafa M.A.Maree</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1n b\u1ed9 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 : Mohammed T.S.Asmar</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 (20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7) :</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Naim R.N.Abuaker, Ramzi S.A.Fahkouri, Ahmad M.A.Qatmish, Mahmoud M.N.Abuwarda, Mohanad S.A.Fannoun, Mahmoud A.N.Yousef, Yousef M.M.Alashhab, Mohammed A.A.Obaid, Mousa B.M.Farawi, Hani S.A.Abdallah, Oday I.M.Dabbagh, Shehab R.I.Qymbor, Mohammed H.M.Alassa, Mohammed A.M.Khalil, Mohammed B.A.Rashid, Saato Ampntel Salam Fouflias, Michel Milad Termanini, Mohammad El-Kayed, Omar El Cherif, Mohammed A.I.Afmed.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-191891.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-191891.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i U21 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/le-boc-tham-lai-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-dien-ra-vao-ngay-nao-292-191911.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/le-boc-tham-lai-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-dien-ra-vao-ngay-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/le-boc-tham-lai-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-dien-ra-vao-ngay-nao-292-191911.html\">L\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o?</span><br>\r\nL\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia m\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf Kuala Lumpur (Malaysia).</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang-168-191908.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang-168-191908.html\">B\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018: Khi ph\u00e9p vua c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i thua l\u1ec7 l\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nCh\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh song cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4583","checkdouble":"191940"},{"date":"21:33 24/07","title":"\u0110T Olympic Indonesia \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/20/dt-olympic-indonesia-dat-muc-tieu-rat-cao-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, \u0110T Olympic Indonesia \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao trong m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 khi mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>\u0110T Olympic Indonesia \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Indonesia \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Indonesia \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau r\u1ea5t cao t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/23/DT-Olympic-Indonesia-dat-muc-tieu-rat-cao-tai-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Luis Milla k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Olympic Indonesia v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, HLV Luis Milla \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft cho Olympic Indonesia. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho ASIAD 2018. Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u00a0v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi l\u00e0 Bahrain, CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean v\u00e0 Uzbekistan. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Indonesia \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 chung cu\u1ed9c sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Bahrain 0-1, h\u00f2a CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean v\u00e0 Uzbekistan c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, trong 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 6 v\u1eeba qua, \u0110T Olympic Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ecd x\u00e1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 thua s\u00e1t n\u00fat v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Luis Milla \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Singapore v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed13-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Indonesia l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ASIAD. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 4 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong danh s\u00e1ch v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T Olympic Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp ng\u00f4i sao g\u1ed1c H\u00e0 Lan Stefano Lilipaly, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Muhammad Ridho, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Andritany Ardhiyasa c\u1ee7a Persija Jakarta v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o g\u1ed1c Brazil Alberto Goncalves. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i. Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-mang-luc-luong-rat-manh-sang-doi-dau-u23-viet-nam-tai-cup-tu-hung-168-191940.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/doi-thu-mang-luc-luong-rat-manh-sang-doi-dau-u23-viet-nam-tai-cup-tu-hung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/doi-thu-mang-luc-luong-rat-manh-sang-doi-dau-u23-viet-nam-tai-cup-tu-hung-168-191940.html\">\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 mang l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Cup T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, \u0110T U23 Palestine c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 mang m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh sang tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/le-boc-tham-lai-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-dien-ra-vao-ngay-nao-292-191911.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/le-boc-tham-lai-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-dien-ra-vao-ngay-nao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/le-boc-tham-lai-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-dien-ra-vao-ngay-nao-292-191911.html\">L\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o?</span><br>\r\nL\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia m\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf Kuala Lumpur (Malaysia).</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang-168-191908.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/boc-tham-asiad-2018-khi-phep-vua-cung-phai-thua-le-lang-168-191908.html\">B\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018: Khi ph\u00e9p vua c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i thua l\u1ec7 l\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nCh\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh song cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4582","checkdouble":"191941"},{"date":"21:48 24/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m t\u1ea1o \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi th\u00f4ng minh khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/thu-mon-dang-van-lam-khong-nghi-toi-chuyen-thang-thua-khi-len-tuyen.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng coi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 v\u1eeba qua, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ra 20 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u01b0u t\u00fa nh\u1ea5t trong danh s\u00e1ch 30 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n th\u1eafng thua khi l\u00ean tuy h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n th\u1eafng thua khi l\u00ean tuy h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/dmh8243-15324411028441950395411.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m - \u1ea2nh: D\u00e2n Tr\u00ed</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n L\u00e2m s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u2018\u0111\u00e0n em\u2019 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh. Tuy nhi\u00ean anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd coi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\" \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, kh\u00f4ng ai trong \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a nhau. L\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng nhau t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Ai \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh s\u1ebd ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 anh em, L\u00e2m s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, ch\u01a1i m\u00e1u l\u1eeda v\u00ec m\u00e0u c\u1edd s\u1eafc \u00e1o\", th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ec1u 24/7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng c\u0169ng th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n khi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u so v\u1edbi 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n L\u00e2m cho bi\u1ebft: \" Kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec h\u01a1n tu\u1ed5i, kinh nghi\u1ec7m m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 tin. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, gi\u1eef phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn khi gi\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, l\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung. Nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft..<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e2m b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 vinh d\u1ef1 kh\u00ed c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m L\u00e2m v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ed5 v\u0169 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1, h\u00f4m nay th\u00ec L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c em chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb thi \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t trong c\u00e1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam so v\u1edbi t\u1ea1i CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng n\u01a1i anh \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e1 nh\u1ecf, ng\u1eafn, nhanh, c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u1edf d\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f2n \u1edf H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i L\u00e2m hay \u0111\u00e1 d\u00e0i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap L\u00e2m v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c\", th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Vi\u1ec7t ki\u1ec1u Nga th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-thu-olympic-viet-nam-su-tu-tin-cua-thay-park-168-191683.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hang-thu-olympic-viet-nam-su-tu-tin-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hang-thu-olympic-viet-nam-su-tu-tin-cua-thay-park-168-191683.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</span><br />\r\n12 \u2013 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a HLV Park...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4581","checkdouble":"191943"},{"date":"06:59 25/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA 17h00 ng\u00e0y 25/7 (C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-thanh-hoa-vs-slna-17h00-ngay-257-cup-quoc-gia-viet-nam-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA l\u00fac 17h00 ng\u00e0y 25/7 (B\u00e1n k\u1ebft C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span>Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nC\u1ea3 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 SLNA \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f9ng tr\u1ea3i qua giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf V-League 2018 khi t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1 s\u00e2u tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng. C\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m SLNA ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi khu v\u1ef1c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf, c\u00f2n FLC Thanh H\u00f3a r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 10, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh v\u00e0 x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i sinh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 leo cao tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng V-League 2018. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i 7 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi 5 th\u1eafng, 2 h\u00f2a th\u00ec SLNA l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi 8 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi chi\u1ebfm lu\u00f4n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh FLC Thanh H\u00f3a.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA 17h00 ng\u00e0y 257 C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA 17h00 ng\u00e0y 257 C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/thanh-hoa-slna.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thanh H\u00f3a vs SLNA</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng SLNA \u1edf v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. Tuy v\u1eady, s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, Pape Omar s\u1ebd gi\u00fap FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 trong hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf V-League g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (h\u00f2a Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00e0 thua H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u \u201cc\u1ee9u c\u00e1nh\u201d cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 SLNA. V\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd mu\u1ed1n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 hai HLV c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u00ean gi\u1ed1ng nhau l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV-League ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o qu\u00e3ng ngh\u1ec9 kh\u00e1 d\u00e0i. V\u00f2ng 21 s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 kh\u1edfi tranh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 8/9. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng C\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMu\u1ed1n v\u1eady, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tranh th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1i \u0111a l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1edbi l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u1edf s\u00e2n Vinh\u201d, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi SLNA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng t\u00ean c\u1ee7a SLNA t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung cao nh\u1ea5t cho chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Thanh H\u00f3a \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. M\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0\u201d.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nFLC.TH: B\u1eedu Ng\u1ecdc, \u0110\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ed3ng, Ti\u1ebfn Th\u00e0nh, Xu\u00e2n Th\u00e0nh, Xu\u00e2n H\u01b0ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ea1i, Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecbnh, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00f9ng, Rimario.<br>\r\nSLNA: V\u0169 H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u00ecnh Ho\u00e0ng, Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Kh\u00e1nh, Xu\u00e2n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n B\u00ecnh, Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, Olaha, Dwayne.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4580","checkdouble":"191951"},{"date":"19:55 24/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 24/7: MU nh\u1eafm sao tuy\u1ec3n Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-247-mu-nham-sao-tuyen-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 24/7.</h2><h2>MU nh\u1eafm sao tuy\u1ec3n Croatia\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 247 MU nh\u1eafm sao tuy\u1ec3n Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 247 MU nh\u1eafm sao tuy\u1ec3n Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-127,-tin-nong-chuyen-nhuong-he-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 24/7: MU nh\u1eafm ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Ante Rebic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Independent, Man United \u0111ang b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Ante Rebic c\u1ee7a Croatia. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh khi c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Croatia l\u1ecdt t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng trong hai th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Willian v\u00e0 Gareth Bale n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Rebic.</div>\r\n<h2>Barca \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Malcom</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Goal \u0111\u01b0a tin Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi ra kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 41 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Malcom t\u1eeb Bordeaux. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Roma sau khi kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai b\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn. Nh\u01b0ng Barca \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eabng tay tr\u00ean trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 Malcom \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 50 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Boateng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Suddeutsche Zeitung mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 50 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u1ebfu b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng. T\u00e2n HLV Niko Kovac s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ra \u0111i sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. PSG l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Boateng l\u00fac n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Henry \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Aston Villa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Daily Star kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Thierry Henry c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Aston Villa. Henry hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf HLV Steve Bruce t\u1ea1i Villa Park.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ra gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Sport \u0111\u01b0a tin Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Willian. Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 60 tri\u1ec7u euro g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u01b0ng b\u1ecb Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30.</div>\r\n<h2>Juve v\u00e0 Milan \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u1ed7 Bonucci &ndash; Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus v\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 trao \u0111\u1ed5i g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Milan \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi CEO Beppe Marotta c\u1ee7a Juve nh\u01b0ng hai b\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Juve \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Higuain ra \u0111i sau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Bonucci d\u1eabu cho ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y m\u1edbi r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Juventus Arena h\u1ed3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-247-bat-ngo-voi-doi-thu-lon-nhat-cua-man-city-mua-sau-184-191872.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 24/7: B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Man City m\u00f9a sau</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-237-vuot-mat-mu-barca-sap-no-bom-tan-tu-chelsea-184-191851.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 23/7: V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU, Barca s\u1eafp n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n t\u1eeb Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4579","checkdouble":"191937"},{"date":"21:36 24/07","title":"Chelsea l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Bayern","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/24/chelsea-len-ke-hoach-chieu-mo-sao-bayern.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thiago Alcantara \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 nh\u1eb1m gia c\u1ed1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.</h2><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Thiago</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Bayern Munich \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n chia tay ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i. HLV Niko Kovac d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u1eaft g\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i Allianz Arena.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThiago Alcantara \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Man United h\u1ed3i n\u0103m 2013. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thiago Alcantara\" title=\"Thiago Alcantara\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/chelsea-len-ke-hoach-chieu-mo-sao-bayern.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Thiago Alcantara</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i Thiago s\u00e1t sao trong v\u00f2ng 12 th\u00e1ng qua. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1edd ESPN kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea v\u00e0 Man United b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBayern Munich kh\u00e1 c\u1edfi m\u1edf trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra \u0111i. V\u1edbi 9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, HLV Kovac c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 Thiago ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Thiago</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Allianz Arena. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Do \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Thiago, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi kho\u1ea3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Man United \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 chi ti\u00eau kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh tay \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Fred gia nh\u1eadp Man United v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ednh l\u00e0 47 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Barcelona. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u0169ng mong m\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0a ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 Camp Nou sau 5 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-247-mu-nham-sao-tuyen-croatia-184-191937.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 24/7: MU nh\u1eafm sao tuy\u1ec3n Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/3-thuong-vu-co-the-se-no-tai-man-united-trong-nhung-ngay-toi-187-191935.html\">3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd n\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i Man United trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4578","checkdouble":"191939"},{"date":"18:20 24/07","title":"James Rodriguez s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Bayern h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/james-rodriguez-se-khong-roi-bayern-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zidane \u0111i v\u00e0 Lopetegui \u0111\u1ebfn, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Colombia m\u1edf ra. Nh\u01b0ng theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn James Rodriguez \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern Munich m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nJames kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u h\u1ebft<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i trong b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 2 n\u0103m, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ban \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i H\u00f9m x\u00e1m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Real Madrid &ndash; Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p. Theo th\u00f4ng tin ban \u0111\u1ea7u, James t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 x\u01b0a, khi HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, anh cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Bayern.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Bayern Munich. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. CLB cho th\u1ea5y t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern Munich m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, thay v\u00ec quay l\u1ea1i Real\" title=\"James Rodriguez s\u1ebd ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/james-rodriguez-co-the-tro-lai-real-ngay-mua-he-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>James Rodriguez \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern Munich m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, thay v\u00ec quay l\u1ea1i Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1ea1i Real Madrid, d\u00f9 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho l\u1eafm. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 36 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f9ng 42 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n khi l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 CLB t\u00f4i g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap C1, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 James Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng, cho th\u1ea5y anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Bayern Munich m\u1edbi l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p d\u00e0nh cho anh v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a 2 CLB, James Rodriguez \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern Munich trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn quy\u1ec1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2019.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-muc-tieu-gia-mem-ma-real-madrid-co-the-chieu-mo-thay-vi-eden-hazard-180-191925.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/3-muc-tieu-gia-mem-ma-real-madrid-co-the-chieu-mo-thay-vi-eden-hazard.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-muc-tieu-gia-mem-ma-real-madrid-co-the-chieu-mo-thay-vi-eden-hazard-180-191925.html\">3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e1 m\u1ec1m m\u00e0 Real Madrid c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 thay v\u00ec Eden Hazard</span><br>\r\nSau khi chia tay Ronaldo, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Hazard nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-real-madrid-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-180-191869.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/5/24/tan-binh-real-madrid-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-real-madrid-ha-muc-tieu-vo-dich-champions-league-180-191869.html\">T\u00e2n binh Real Madrid h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng 18 tu\u1ed5i Vinicius Junior t\u1ecf ra tham v\u1ecdng ngay sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 46 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Santiago de Bernabeu.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4577","checkdouble":"191933"},{"date":"06:32 25/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Barcelona \"c\u01b0\u1edbp\" th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u0169i AS Roma","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c sau AS Roma nh\u01b0ng Barcelona l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom khi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi h\u01a1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom t\u1eeb Bordeaux v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 41 tri\u1ec7u euro (c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam 1 tri\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam). Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Nou Camp.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/chinh-thuc-barcelona-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-malcom.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Barcelona chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Malcom.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Malcom v\u1edbi Barca s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2023. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 ba c\u1ee7a Barcelona trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, sau nh\u1eefng Arthur Melo (Gremio - 31 tri\u1ec7u) v\u00e0 Clement Lenglet (Sevilla - 35.9).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Malcom tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a AS Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u euro. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Barca kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n m\u00e0 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u0169ng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n khi\u1ebfn Malcom kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Roma.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Malcom l\u00e0 ai?<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sinh ng\u00e0y 26/2/1997 t\u1ea1i Sao Paulo (Brazil), Malcom Filipe Silva de Oliveira \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Brazil hi\u1ec7n nay. Malcom g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Malcom gia nh\u1eadp Bordeaux n\u0103m 18 tu\u1ed5i. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, Malcom ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 19 b\u00e0n sau 86 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1eebng g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap \u0110T U20 Brazil gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00e1 qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i U20 World Cup 2015.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barcelona h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca-180-191808.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\">\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\">G\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n 3, Barca quy\u1ebft mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ajax-gui-canh-bao-danh-thep-toi-barca-180-191626.html\">Nh\u0103m nhe sao tr\u1ebb, Barca nh\u1eadn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o g\u1eaft t\u1eeb Ajax</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chan-mu-pogba-co-dong-thai-san-sang-dau-quan-cho-barca-172-191187.html\">Ch\u00e1n M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-sap-co-tan-binh-thu-hai-trong-he-2018-180-190985.html\">H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Barca trong h\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nN.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4576","checkdouble":"191946"},{"date":"18:39 24/07","title":"Ozil b\u1ecb \u0110\u1ee9c ru\u1ed3ng b\u1ecf? \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 lo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/ozil-bi-duc-ruong-bo-da-co-tho-nhi-ky-lo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau nh\u1eefng scandal g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean ph\u1ed1 \u1edf qu\u00ea g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3, sau khi anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nOzil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh danh n\u01a1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sinh ra v\u00e0 l\u1edbn l\u00ean t\u1ea1i Gelsenkirchen, \u0110\u1ee9c &ndash; Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014. Tuy nhi\u00ean, gia \u0111\u00ecnh anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady sau khi b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00ec nh\u1eefng c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c, qu\u1ed1c gia t\u1ed5 ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ozil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch l\u1ea5y t\u00ean anh \u0111\u1eb7t cho t\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n. D\u00f9 v\u1eady trong 2 b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh m\u00e0 Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c treo, anh m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 CLB Arsenal.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, con ph\u1ed1 mang t\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y &ndash; &ldquo;Mesut Ozil Street&rdquo; n\u1eb1m \u1edf qu\u1eadn Devrek c\u1ee7a Zonguldak, ph\u00eda b\u1eafc Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 ghi nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch m\u00e0 Ozil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Mustafa Semerci x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t, v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng Ozil ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u00f9ng T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 Erdogan.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mesut Ozil, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3: &ldquo;Khi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. Khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i l\u00e0 th\u1eb1ng nh\u1eadp c\u01b0 g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5&rdquo;. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u1ecd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, khi cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y &ldquo;lu\u00f4n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n d\u00e2n nh\u1eadp c\u01b0&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>C\u00f9ng xem nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean ph\u1ed1 \u1edf Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean ph\u1ed1 \u1edf qu\u00ea g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean ph\u1ed1 \u1edf qu\u00ea g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean ph\u1ed1 \u1edf qu\u00ea g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean ph\u1ed1 \u1edf qu\u00ea g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/183557-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u1ee5p c\u00f9ng T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng TNK \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean ph\u1ed1 \u1edf qu\u00ea g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn Mesut Ozil Street</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mesut Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean ph\u1ed1 \u1edf qu\u00ea g\u1ed1c Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>2 b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c treo \u1edf th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n ph\u00eda b\u1eafc Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ozil-tiep-tuc-bi-danh-hoi-dong-tu-tuyen-duc-421-191879.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/ozil-tiep-tuc-bi-danh-hoi-dong-tu-tuyen-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ozil-tiep-tuc-bi-danh-hoi-dong-tu-tuyen-duc-421-191879.html\">Ozil ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1eeb tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Mesut Ozil sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh quay l\u1ea1i m\u00e0u \u00e1o n\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mesut-ozil-cay-dang-bo-tuyen-that-bai-cua-ca-nen-bong-da-421-191850.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/Lothar-Matthaus-chi-trich-Mesut-Ozil-tham-te-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mesut-ozil-cay-dang-bo-tuyen-that-bai-cua-ca-nen-bong-da-421-191850.html\">Mesut Ozil cay \u0111\u1eafng b\u1ecf tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c: Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00ecnh n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1m ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u1ea1nh l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4575","checkdouble":"191936"},{"date":"21:08 24/07","title":"Bakayoko g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t Sarri \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/bakayoko-gap-mat-sarri-doi-ra-di.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tiemoue Bakayoko \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi HLV Maurizio Sarri r\u1eb1ng anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Chelsea ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Bakayoko mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb Monaco v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Estadio Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1edbi Bakayoko. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay th\u1ebf Steven N&rsquo;Zonzi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m nay kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bakayoko\" title=\"Bakayoko\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/bakayoko-gap-mat-sarri-doi-ra-di.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bakayoko mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSevilla \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Bakayoko. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sevilla r\u1eb1ng anh mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi La Liga thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, Bakayoko c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1edbi HLV Sarri r\u1eb1ng anh mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho Bakayoko l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t cho su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Chelsea. Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Sarri v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 Jorginho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c sau khi Sarri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBakayoko c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t t\u1eeb Ross Barkley. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau khi b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBakayoko hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00f9ng Chelsea t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8. Anh c\u0169ng v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay cho Jorginho \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Perth Glory h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Hai v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-chelsea-nen-het-minh-vi-cuoc-tai-hop-sarri-higuain-172-191931.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Chelsea n\u00ean h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00ec cu\u1ed9c t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Sarri &ndash; Higuain</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-trung-ve-nguoi-italia-len-45-trieu-bang-172-191927.html\">Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia l\u00ean 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4574","checkdouble":"191938"},{"date":"22:54 24/07","title":"B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb MU tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf ICC 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/bo-doi-sao-tre-mu-tuyen-bo-san-sang-toa-sang-o-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb Axel Tuanzebe v\u00e0 Timothy Fosu-Mensah quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Man United.</h2><h2>Tuanzebe quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao \u0111\u1ed9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9. Anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi AC Milan, Liverpool, Real Madrid v\u00e0 Bayern Munich tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Tuanzebe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Aston Villa thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. Anh ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford sau khi g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 4. V\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi San Jose Earthquakes, Tuanzebe t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb MU tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i sao tr\u1ebb MU tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/bo-doi-sao-tre-mu-tuyen-bo-san-sang-toa-sang-o-icc-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sao tr\u1ebb MU quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf ICC 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t. Tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ph\u1ea5n ch\u1ea5n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trong \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec. Khi tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh trong th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf v\u1edbi th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Fosu-Mensah hy v\u1ecdng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Crystal Palace. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 24 l\u1ea7n cho \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Palace tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u01a1i \u1edf Palace m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc mang l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ed1t. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i \u1edf Premier League. T\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb HLV Roy Hodgson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Man United. T\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi, thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Mourinho v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng hi\u1ec7n nay\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-247-mu-nham-sao-tuyen-croatia-184-191937.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 24/7: MU nh\u1eafm sao tuy\u1ec3n Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-van-de-cua-mu-sau-tran-hoa-nhat-san-jose-earthquakes-172-191926.html\">Nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a MU sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1ea1t San Jose Earthquakes</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4573","checkdouble":"191942"}]}